# save_params() (src/user_interface_menus/_menu_helper.py) rewrites this
# file with native line endings (LF on POSIX, CRLF on Windows) every time
# the interface loads/saves menu params, including during test runs. Pin
# the git blob to LF so running tests/the interface on Linux (Pi, Fedora)
# doesn't produce a line-ending-only diff against the Windows-authored copy.
config/uiconfig.txt text eol=lf
